{
  "stem": "25348.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At that time, there were seven million foreign workers in Germany, and they became more cautious [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and frightened of the foreign workers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The reason being that they had an emergency draft for boys over 15, I think, and for old men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were no men in the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were on the-- on the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they tried to flush out from unimportant centers, such as private household, the people to more important for them, more important-- something relevant to the war industry.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What also happened, I told you that the Winklers were not Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a non-party members, they did not qualify for a domestic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Frau Winkler told me that herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are not party people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had-- every block in Germany was blessed-- and I'm saying this sarcastically-- with a house warden.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "House wardens were usually Nazis who acted as spies, more or less, to inform on the tenants.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a visit like this frequently, mostly under the pretext to watch whether it's fire safe, whether it's this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, he came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This chap was called [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Andreas ?] and he asked Frau Winkler, how long has this Pole-- this Polish girl been with you?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, 10 months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He scribbled 10 months, went through every room to pretend that it was fire security he had in mind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after a few days-- it was before Christmas-- I got a message that my job has been canceled with the Winklers, and I have to report to a hotel in Hartha.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a very far away place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember, but it was about 20 or 30 kilometers from the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to report to a hotel called [NON ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
